snippet.title: Birds and Saws [ iOS/Android ]
snippet.description:
Download: https://appsto.re/i6B85zB
Twitter: https://twitter.com/BirdsAndSaws

Simple and addictive oldschool arcade style casual game.

--- INSTRUCTIONS ---

- Choose your favorite character
- Tap left or right to Jump
- Avoid saw blades
- Master your skills for the top records on the leaderboards


--- FEATURES ---

++ Colorful Retro Graphics
++ Sweeping Chiptune Soundtrack
++ Unlockable Characters
++ Game Center Leaderboard & Achievements

★  MUSIC  ★
★ RoccoW ★
